Uses of Package
collections

Packages that use collections
collections This package contains interfaces, implementations, and other utilities for working with Collections and Maps. 
 

Classes in collections used by collections
BoundedMap
          A capacity restricted Map.
BoundedQueue
          A capacity restricted Queue.
FIFOMap
          A LinkedHashMap implementation of BoundedMap which removes stale mappings in insertion/first-in-first-out order.
ForwardingPeekingIterator
          A PeekingIterator which forwards all its method calls to another PeekingIterator.
LinkedBoundedQueue
          A linked list implementation of BoundedQueue.
LRUMap
          A LinkedHashMap implementation of BoundedMap which removes stale mappings in access/least-recently-used order.
PriorityBoundedQueue
          An implementation of BoundedQueue backed by a PriorityQueue.
PriorityDeque
          An unbounded priority Deque based on a modified red-black tree.
PriorityQueue
          An unbounded priority Queue based on a modified red-black tree.
SortedList
          A sorted List based on a modified red-black tree.
UnmodifiableListIterator
          A ListIterator that does not support remove(), add(), and set(E).
UnmodifiablePeekingIterator
          A PeekingIterator that does not support remove().
